{"tid":2504294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"望著今日嘅Supper Moment同香港電台，就好似見證住香港嘅淪落一樣","createTime":"2021-04-25T18:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T14:22:14.000Z","uid":48124,"like":134,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"0add2b32671350750679ab0239eddf709879e5ce","tid":2504294,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T18:41:43.000Z","msg":"明明兩者都昔日好有型，喺行內立下左極高嘅製作/表演水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但前者因為所講「搵食」/「上位」，完全變咗冇晒靈魂嘅牆頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaR5SV9JiejavtpjjKx6rHsh9UUU3nXTMB4RSHWjXwNcs?filename=FGx5mOk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFGx5mOk.png&h=826e78dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcs5AwPvYAUWb23gdBrdRuepZin12qfiCs8czBwyFDuW7?filename=hs9GEz3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhs9GEz3.png&h=f036ec5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmURHFUVea9H68qnNv2m1M81wpopekPKjVEbZuGgDS8uy5?filename=LnhdvGN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnhdvGN.png&h=049ab876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個表演作為supper多年fans真係柒到不能直視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全侮辱緊咁多年嚟支持過佢哋人嘅品味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後者因為極權嘅爪牙，同樣地只係得返軀殼<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTzhMAvZby8SJyFVdfLzcMWMFT5vrPPscu9atQs5Q7qEe?filename=PGFuOuL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGFuOuL.jpg&h=49d70902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感覺香港會有越來越多呢類「北韓式」口味嘅節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慢慢將香港人最引以為傲嘅文化取替"},{"pid":"79932df876c41c6aba776a3d68bc461a1b9faa47","tid":2504294,"uid":154486,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T22:12:05